- @title = 'Hansard not found'
%p
  Here's how we interpreted the reference:
%ul
  %li
    %span House:
    = @reference.house.to_s.capitalize
  %li
    %span Date:
    = @reference.date_to_s
  %li
    %span Volume:
    = @reference.volume
  %li
    %span Start column:
    = @reference.column
  %li
    %span Type:
    - if @reference.is_written_answer?
      written answer
    - elsif @reference.is_written_statement?
      written statement

%p
  Either we don't have that Hansard in our database, or there is no Hansard that matches the reference:
%ul
  %li
    = @query
%p
  Try browsing our
  = link_to("sittings in #{@reference.year}",  "/sittings/#{@reference.year}") +'.'
